HEADWORD: girlfriend
<hw>girl"friend`</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>any female friend;
<as>as, Mary and her <ex>girlfriend</ex> organized the party</as>.</def>
<wns>[wns=1]</wns>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>a girl or young woman with whom a man is
romantically involved; <as>as, his <ex>girlfriend</ex> kicked him
out</as>.</def> <wns>[wns=2]</wns>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> girl, lady friend.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Girlhood</ent>⟦br⟧
